@{PARD}
@{B}Golem, Rat, Stone Ecology:@{UB}@{PAR}

Rat Golems are not natural creatures, and play no part in the world's ecology.
They neither eat nor sleep, and "live" until their bodies are destroyed, usually
in combat.@{PAR}

